08-08T06:06:54.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲信on9保皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e9e34349c4b8c47eeb08f406ebd05e9caf86510","tid":1431792,"uid":85694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:07:48.000Z","msg":"我分析你聽<br />\n最無恥點解要你延遲示威<br />\n因為國家未派錢落黎比佢搞運動<br />\n佢而家策略係拖字訣<br />\n班人一拎到錢就會用盡一切方法搞散個運動<br />\n林病要解決問題 根本一早做獨立調查就解決<br />\n而家班人係唔想比示威者有機會贏<br />\n等你班示威人死哂心佢繼續高壓同欺騙式統治<br />\n所以千萬不能停止示威 直至佢地跪企含<br />\n有幾多做幾多 兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64d7a40a20a8ba4534b6dc07e8b276bf915cae6","tid":1431792,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:41:22.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}